description:
We believe in the service of the Lord’s Supper as more than a tradition or an act of worship. The #Communion service symbolizes God’s will for His Church–of unity among the body of believers, as unified as the bread, broken between Christ and His closest 12. Click the link in our stories to learn more about what #Adventists believe about #theLordsSupper. #Devotionalthought  #Biblestudy #AdventistBeliefs 

To watch the full episode, paste the link into your browser: https://youtu.be/0bZSXyrblr4
